### 获取所有天气预测
GET https://localhost:7000/api/weatherforecast

### 获取特定ID的天气预测
GET https://localhost:7000/api/weatherforecast/1

### 获取所有学生
GET https://localhost:7000/api/students

### 获取特定ID的学生
GET https://localhost:7000/api/students/1

### 创建新学生
POST https://localhost:7000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "新学生",
  "age": 23,
  "email": "newstudent@example.com",
  "major": "软件工程"
}

### 更新学生信息
PUT https://localhost:7000/api/students/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "张三（已更新）",
  "age": 21,
  "email": "zhangsan_updated@example.com",
  "major": "计算机科学与技术"
}

### 删除学生
DELETE https://localhost:7000/api/students/1

### 搜索学生（按专业）
GET https://localhost:7000/api/students/search\?major\=计算机

### 搜索学生（按年龄）
GET https://localhost:7000/api/students/search\?minAge\=20

### 搜索学生（组合条件）
GET https://localhost:7000/api/students/search\?major\=数学\&minAge\=20

### 健康检查
GET https://localhost:7000/api/health
